com.percussion.loader.ui
Interface IPSConfigPanel

All Known Implementing Classes:
PSConfigPanel, PSExtractorConfigPanel, PSItemExtractorConfigPanel
public interface IPSConfigPanel

An interface that must be implemented from all editor panels written for the configuration dialog.
